# Default deny: ~/.codex contains auth, sessions, caches, logs, and local state.
*

# Track public repo files only.
!.gitignore
!AGENTS.md
!README.md
!config.toml
!skills/
!skills/coding-confidant/
!skills/coding-confidant/**
!skills/trend-researcher/
!skills/trend-researcher/**
!skills/insights/
!skills/insights/**

# Never publish local-only or generated artifacts.
AGENTS.md.bak-*
**/.DS_Store
skills/**/_docs/
skills/**/_docs/**
skills/**/_log_inlineMark/
skills/**/_log_inlineMark/**
skills/**/__pycache__/
skills/**/*.pyc
